media-cleanup - Media Organization Cleanup

USAGE:
    media-cleanup

DESCRIPTION:
    Clean up and organize media files. Ensures media is organized
    consistently and easy to find. Processes files in /media/output.

FUNCTIONS:
    - Find all links in by-time and by-tag directories
    - Identify unique filenames
    - Map files and handle duplicates
    - Remove underscores from filenames
    - Convert .jpeg extensions to .jpg

NOTE:
    Runtime approximately 1 hour for full processing.

EXAMPLES:
    media-cleanup
